Watch the Rolling Stones Rock ‘You Can’t Always Get What You Want’ (Virtually)Photo: Variety Photo: Variety Image 1 of / 1 Caption Close Watch the Rolling Stones Rock ‘You Can’t Always Get What You Want’ (Virtually) 1 / 1 Back to GalleryClick here to read the full article.
Nearly 60 years into their collective existence, it’s rare for the Rolling Stones to do something musically that they haven’t really done before — but that certainly happened on Saturday night for their performance of their 1969 classic “You Can’t Always Get What You Want” on Global Citizen’s “Together at Home” concert.
“We’re hugely disappointed to have to postpone the tour.
We are sorry to all the fans who were looking forward to it as much as we were, but the health and safety of everyone has to take priority,” the group said in a statement.
